==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Transliterate
<hw>Trans*lit"er*ate</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>v. t.</pos> <ety>[Pref.
<ets>trans-</ets> + L. <ets>litera</ets>, <ets>littera</ets>
letter.]</ety> <def>To express or represent in the characters of another
alphabet; <as>as, to <ex>transliterate</ex> Sanskrit words by means of
English letters</as>.</def> <rj><au>A. J. Ellis.</au></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

